data.description:
Don't miss out on this exceptional property! Impeccably maintained, this two-story home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, an open floor plan, and a finished walkout, providing over 2800 sq.ft. of living space. Recent updates include a spacious kitchen with a central island, stainless steel appliances, and Schlabach cabinets backed by lifetime warranties. The property features new shingles installed in 2017, a newer deck, a brand-new furnace added in 2023, a wireless Culligan reverse osmosis system, and a radon detection/mitigation system. Enjoy the contemporary touch of sleek porcelain flooring throughout the main floor.

Act quickly, as this property is sure to be in high demand. Schedule your showing today before it's gone!

All showings must be accompanied by a licensed agent. BATVAI
